# SEO Redirect Rules for graver-studio.uz
# Priority: HTTP → HTTPS, www → non-www, trailing slash normalization

# 1. HTTP to HTTPS (all requests)
http://graver-studio.uz/*  https://graver-studio.uz/:splat  301
http://www.graver-studio.uz/*  https://graver-studio.uz/:splat  301

# 2. www to non-www (HTTPS)
https://www.graver-studio.uz/*  https://graver-studio.uz/:splat  301

# 3. Trailing slash normalization (remove trailing slash for consistency)
# Note: Cloudflare Pages handles this via SPA routing, but explicit rules help
/ru/  /ru  301
/uz/  /uz  301
/ru/blog/  /ru/blog  301
/uz/blog/  /uz/blog  301

